column1: NGR is from 1950s record and is Boulters Lock. Altitudes match

The 1913 readings are the same as Maidenhead Belmont Road, which is a record covering that year only but does have a reading for January. Belmont Road is 2.5km from Boulters Lock and there is no way of seeing if the observers are connected. On balance the Boulters Lock readings seem more credible.
